quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,87,"Atari kumpuhwe zivuye ku Muremyi wawe, mu vy’ukuri imigisha yayo iri hejuru yawe ni mininiya cane"
  17,88,"Vuga uti:- naho bokoranya abantu bose hamwe n’ibisigo vyose kugira ngo bazane ivyoba bimeze nkiyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, ntibari gushobora kuyizana iyimeze nkiyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, naho bofashanya bamwe n’abandi"
  17,89,"Ntankeka twaramenyesheje abantu muburyo bwinshi buri muri iki gitabu ceranda ca Qur’ani kuburorero butagira uko bungana, mugabo abantu benshi barahakana atari ubuhakanyi bwabo gusa"
  17,90,"Baravuze bati:- twebwe ntidu shobora kukwemera kugeza aho uzo tuzanira isoko ry’amazi mri iki gisagara cacu"
  17,91,"Canke ube ufise umurima w’ivyamwa vy’imitende hamwe n’imizabibu, hanyuma ucishe mwo inzuzi hagati yayo ashunguruka ari menshi cane"
  17,92,"Canke udusenyurire ijuru ribe ibimanyu manyu nkuko wavyivugiye, canke utuzanire Imana hamwe n’Abamarayika tubibonere amaso kuyandi"
  17,93,"Canke ube ufise inzu y’inzahabu, canke uduge mw’ijuru, kandi ntituzo kwemera kw’uko kuduga kwawe utatumanuriye igitabu tugisome, nawe vuga uti:- nihaninahazwe Imana yanje ntagatifu kuko jewe sinari kuba atari uko nd’intumwa y’Imana gusa, sindi umumarayika canke Imana"
  17,94,"Ntacabujije abantu kwemera Imana y’ukuri mugihe wabashikira n’uburongozi atari uko bavuze bati:- mbega Imana ihora irungika umuntu kuba intumwa yayo"
  17,95,"Vuga uti:- iyo haba ng’aha kw’Isi Abamarayika bagenda bitonze, ntankeka twari kuba manurira kuva mw’Ijuru Abamarayika kuba arizo ntumwa zabo"
  17,96,"Vuga uti:- Imana irahagije kuba ariyo cabona hagati yanje na mwebwe, mu vy’ukuri niyo ibazi neza abashumvyi biwe, kandi iraba bona"